name: The fifth incarnation. Mammoth.
description:
The desire to live a long full life led me into the body of a mammoth. Being an only child, I was surrounded by the love and care of my parents. Happy childhood quickly flew by and was replaced by an interesting adult life.

We moved around a lot in search of delicious deciduous trees. Somehow, in a dense forest, I ran into Her nose to nose. It was love at first sight. Mutual love. We were made for each other. Soon a beautiful baby appeared. 

Years passed. We have traveled great distances. And there was no happier family in the world than ours. 

And this story ended on an autumn day. We were crossing a mountain pass. I was walking ahead, accidentally stepped on a shaky stone and fell down. Two legs were broken. I lay and watched the approach of previously unseen creatures. They came up and stabbed me with sharp sticks. 

In this incarnation, I have known the love and joy of fatherhood. And I also met a man…
